title: Ep. - 287 - DOWN TO EARTH WITH ZAC EFRON SEASON FINALE OF REAL HOUSEWIVES OF NEW YORK
description:
Brian Volk-Weiss is Executive Producer of Down to Earth with Zac Efron, a documentary revolving around Efron and a wellness entreprenuer Darin Olien traveling around the world to France, Puerto Rico, London, Iceland, Costa Rica, Peruand Sardinia, and focuses on themes of travel, life experience, nature, green energyand sustainable living practices.

 

Ashley Hearon-Smith & Keri Setaro, co-hosts of Momtourage Podcast review the season finale of Real Housewives of New York.
